		<title>Parents should not be allowed to impose their religion on children</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://atheism-vs-islam.com/index.php/child-abuse-in-islam/252-parents-should-not-be-allowed-to-impose-their-religion-on-children"/>
